patthana17.33:1.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ ajjhattārammaṇaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho naajjhattārammaṇo
patthana17.33:1.1_1: dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …. Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… aññamaññe tīṇi …pe… avigate cha.
